# claude2026-actions.twlist
#
# Verb sub-categorization. kimmo tells us a word is a verb in some
# tense; this tells us what KIND of action it represents. Useful for
# grammars that want to fill specific action slots ("a thinking-verb
# in past tense" rather than just "any past-tense verb").

